data.description: Legal 3 Flat building in Bronzeville with 2 bedroom/2 baths in each unit. 2 units have tenants in place with leases. Garden unit could use a little TLC. All Units were rehabbed about 2 years ago. Move in and have the tenants pay your mortgage or keep and add to your rental portfolio. Private Off street parking in the back of building. All the units have an open floor concept with kitchen island and gas fireplaces, hardwood flooring on 1nd & 2nd floor units, SS Appliances, central air. On a block with new construction. Pre-Approved Buyers only. Schedule your appointments today. Sold As-Is. Motivated Seller!
